   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00003"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beer
                     Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine>aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb44374">St. Moritz</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1061">Engadin</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb52032">Hotel du lac</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00002"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb298283"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien, XVIII, Sternwartestr. 71</rs>.</hi></rs></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00003"/><date when="1913-07-23">23. 7. 913</date></dateline><salute>lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>heute fahren wir nach <rs ref="#pmb45260" type="place">Brioni</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb2238" type="person">Lili</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eit ein paar Tagen dort –<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreiben Sie mir doch ein Wort dahin. Es war eine etwas unruhig-ruhige Zeit. Sie
               haben wohl kein<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönes Wetter gehabt bis heut – <pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00002"/>nun
                  wir<unclear>ds</unclear> hoffentlich be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er, – überall. Wir grüßen Sie alle
               herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
